Guide for Docking station for Offline device, Pi 4 Model 4B:

Items needed for the build:
* Small screwdriver and 6 pcs of M2 x 16 mm screws.
* The 5 printed parts from the 3D files (optional also the dummy lid).
* An official Raspberry PI 4 USB-power supply.
* A HDMI- cable with micro-HDMI connector. Manufacturer: Zhonghua, Brand: TWOZOH, Model: ‎HD-012-1.0M
